{"tid":651261,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱狗連app都有，對child登對抗","createTime":"2018-05-03T03:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T10:03:58.000Z","uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8651d2454b8e600b250e8c089840b79b3f051fa3","tid":651261,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:29:41.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰：「熱血社區，義民之地。」當下，我們雖未能撼動建制、改革不義的制度，我們更應凝聚力量，想辦法在這紛擾的社會活得更好。<br />\n為此，我們即將推出一個社區資訊平台-「熱血社區」手機App，包括「熱血動向」、「街坊討論區」、「社區廣告板」等功能，用家亦可直接通過平台與我們的社區主任聯絡、求助。<br />\n「熱血社區」App現正進行公眾測試，為正式發佈做最好的準備。現請大家一同測試，一起建設我們的熱血社區。<br />\n<br />\n《熱血政治》<br />\n<br />\n第1171集︰熱血社區APP 公眾測試<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/112924_1c37c238695250ff99835e8af3486f16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F112924_1c37c238695250ff99835e8af3486f16.png&h=ae0b87a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1377850893901597db6caeb4dc9e18dce9edebc4","tid":651261,"uid":147871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:34:46.000Z","msg":"@上條當麻"},{"pid":"b4d9f5027a3a35a3ee739b97ce0ca94bfd9f37a6","tid":651261,"uid":105715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接用舊登？<br />\n早洩又被過了一棟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae943e94a9c0501ed0716aab34180d4edab346e","tid":651261,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4d9f5027a3a35a3ee739b97ce0ca94bfd9f37a6","tid":651261,"uid":105715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接用舊登？<br />\n早洩又被過了一棟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:51:28.000Z","msg":"舊登個朵臭<br />\n兩邊一齊做打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c859eadea1aab57de3b80bb6ce4e86c77ceb03","tid":651261,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r